sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant U as User
    participant FE as Next.js UI
    participant API as FastAPI /documents/upload/v2
    participant Q as Celery + Redis
    participant W as Worker upload_v2
    participant ING as Ingestion Service
    participant V as Weaviate
    participant S as Upload Storage

    U->>FE: Select files and confirm upload
    FE->>API: POST multipart files
    API->>Q: send_task(ingest_upload_v2)
    API-->>FE: 202 { jobId, status: queued }

    loop Until terminal state
        FE->>API: GET /documents/upload/v2/{jobId}
        API->>Q: AsyncResult(jobId)
        API-->>FE: queued | running | finished | failed
    end

    Q->>W: Deliver task payload
    W->>ING: Decode and ingest each file
    ING->>V: upsert_chunks(vector records)
    ING->>S: Persist file + metadata artifacts
    W-->>Q: SUCCESS or FAILURE payload
